{"tid":1105090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7歲女童遭到少林寺眾虐殺","createTime":"2019-04-13T15:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T01:20:09.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"933706a020db844b6976b8973653412e36cbcb4a","tid":1105090,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:31:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YP7NLEJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYP7NLEJ.jpg&h=99382555&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n河北省邯鄲的7歲女童於本月7日，在河南登封少林寺小龍武院內習武，入學僅2日離奇死亡。<br />\n<br />\n女童父親父認屍時，發現女兒臉色發紫，而且肚上有被踢痕跡。他又指，查看學校監視影像時，拍攝鏡頭距離女兒較遠，但遠看上去有人將她推倒，懷疑女兒被毆打。"},{"pid":"729dcd9ffe2d5878869fc07a1e66f71934d91318","tid":1105090,"uid":94828,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:32:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DjV33r1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjV33r1.png&h=32a22b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9d6511306a4d7a4d611cb5539a0f37ab5756a18","tid":1105090,"uid":27664,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:34:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係18個金粉餅又或者其中一個方丈做嘅</span>"},{"pid":"66fcfcc14edd979718891ab88fce77809e6038f3","tid":1105090,"uid":3302,"like":8,"dislike":9,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:38:49.000Z","msg":"成隻豬咁 死得好"},{"pid":"d2c14231e349747bf1481d656c5abf5b8d5836f7","tid":1105090,"uid":242872,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:41:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"494554605e90f52550c4a7504eb48e1ad5194dc2","tid":1105090,"uid":41524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:42:01.000Z","msg":"似係好撚串嘅肥西"},{"pid":"ed1b57c610130f8200017afda7e5ee563a353214","tid":1105090,"uid":62321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T15:42:03.000Z","msg":"得罪方丈"},{"pid":"ca0a9aac20a4a143766c308c29e8251fe28692cb","tid":1105090,"uid":29270,"lik